         <t:abstract>
            <t:p>The Ḍawana nafs is an epistle written in <t:placeName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LOC6569Tegray">Tǝgrāy</t:placeName> and sent to <t:persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS9038Susenyos">Susǝnyos</t:persName>
            in the <t:date>early 1620s</t:date>.</t:p>
            <t:p>It is also known in Portuguese, Spanish and Italian abridged versions.</t:p>
         </t:abstract>
         <t:textClass>
            <t:keywords>
               <t:term key="ChristianLiterature" ana="#ChristianLiterature"/>
               <t:term key="Other" ana="#Other"/>
            </t:keywords>
         </t:textClass>
